Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who shot him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop Kikuhara...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a silent night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse was beginnin'
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasaneau setsuna o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitto eien to shinjikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:00:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's darker than black
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Meikyuu no sora
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari o kou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If bite your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoudou ga mushibande yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... Can I... Can I... Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Risei o kakikesu libido
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.71,0:01:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurayami ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.17,0:01:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochikitta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Minikui sugata ni natte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hito no namida kareta nara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi wa boku o dou omou no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotae o oshiete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Makka na chi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NMakka na chi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizuna o nurashiai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yowasa o wakeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NYowasa o wakeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Futari wa ikite yuku no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizu o nameatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sei o teigi shiatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai o musabotte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,DEVILS' LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop Kikuhara...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get to the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to do it in one jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,People are gonna see us, so they might shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's coming from the north!\NUp on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! What are you doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw down your weapons and surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Hurry and throw down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Taira and Lee are on the roof?\NWhat are you doing? Hurry and throw down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Taira and Lee are on the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are they doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move! I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay off the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa? Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Too... dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay... away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me? Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A sedative?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How many cc's of blood will it take to heal him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For just the wound and blood loss, 200cc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, he's gonna need 400cc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Four hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If he used that sedative before he got shot,\Nhe'll have a hard time transforming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take twice as much blood as normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the event that a devil\Nignores the deployment ban,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,if they transform and engage in violence,\Ncause injury, or drink blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,they will be immediately relieved of duty,\Nregardless of their reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They will thenceforth be placed\Nunder strict surveillance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and forbidden to make contact with humans\Nfor the foreseeable future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,400cc is too much for someone your size, Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give him blood, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking to?\NDrop your weapon right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep the riot police busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to close Anzai's wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is... I want to let you drink my blood, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do anything I can to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise... I'll never give you my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not sharp enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself. You might-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Bite down, Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up! Bite my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Taira, they broke through! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Push your arm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,or he'll bite it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move! All of you stay where you-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! We're almost done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a devil on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai. Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So no dying, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The wound is starting to close up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you over there! A little help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look in his pouch and find a tranq.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Inject him when I give the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to save the lives of everybody here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogata?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Be alert! If anything happens, shoot all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two different kinds! Which do I use?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, the thicker one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tranq him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an ambulance here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I think one should be getting here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't give you any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm carrying an injured person!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She was bitten by a devil and lost a lot of blood.\NTake care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the stretcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Armed Officers Instigate Devil Hunting Incident
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Down on your knees, slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes are red!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrest you for everyone's safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're pointing your guns at the wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a stretcher on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We have one devil, male. He's been tranquilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He has...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...no external injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here in a quiet residential neighborhood\Nwhere there seems to be an incident involving devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any details yet,\Nbut they've called in the riot police,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill the devils!\Nand I understand they've found multiple bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the pests!\Nand I understand they've found multiple bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling on the F Squad private channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Section 11 wants to hear from your leader, Ishimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Makimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that central government offices,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,starting with the Ministry of\NHealth, Labor, and Welfare,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,were involved with the formation of the CCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to redirect the focus of your investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There are signs that Kikuhara was attempting to\Ntrade out members before this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The old members may be\Npushed out of the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They are vital witnesses in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let them get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't get down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for a mass murderer named Tamaki Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's your...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,your genitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Geni...tor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He was sentenced to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but for some reason,\Nhe was secretly released from jail,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and brought here instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it here. Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In a sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,these are a type of the darkness\Nthat lurks inside all human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here is a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This monster killed 15 people...\Na devil in the truest sense of the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, none of that! You have to lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your attending physician, Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Shirase Hospital Basement 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The special wing for treating devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wounds have closed up, but you lost\Na lot of blood, so you still need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-they didn't bring her with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman with short hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Tsukasa Taira?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here. They admitted her to the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry; her injuries weren't fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Her left arm was broken, with lacerations and\Ndeep bite marks, but it's been treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She lost consciousness,\Nbut she's in stable condition now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand she forced you to bite her own arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I... Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,starting to control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought... there was a light at the end of the tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no time to wait for medical help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If she hadn't closed up that wound then and there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If she hadn't been there for you,\Nyou would be dead. Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She made a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, someone attacked Naoya Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But he escaped with no serious injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And this morning in the\Ndetention center, Kohei Nakamura,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,also known as Zero Four,\Nstole a gun from a guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He was killed in the ensuing gunfight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand Kikuhara visited him yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikuhara?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, we need to immobilize Kikuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put a guard on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Makimura is right, and there are\Nmultiple government agencies pulling the strings,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,then restraining Kikuhara won't stop the murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today, F Squad is dissolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you please reconsider Anzai's punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer Anzai saved my life and Ishimaru's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We did take that into account.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing F Squad is done?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell from the look on Sawazaki's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki's face has always looks\Nexactly the same to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known him a lot longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we've all been suspended for 20 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ishimaru and I are taking pay cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,F Squad will be dissolved,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and the remaining squads\Nwill divide its jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to Public Security General Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You, Asami, will be returning to Division 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And Sawazaki will be\Ntransferred to Division 5, Section 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tied to a desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Lloyd will be transferred to Y Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dr. Yanagi will go back\Nto the hospital we got him from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll miss you all, but this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa! I'm so glad you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Ms. Tsukasa Taira
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who saved you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,he was a devil, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He had long hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's afraid of devils,\Nand they have a really bad reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess they're not all bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of think I'm starting to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That there are devils who can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm the only one...\Nlots of people are getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They've decided on our punishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai will most likely be allowed to resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be placed under strict surveillance,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and prohibited from seeing\Nhis human victim for the foreseeable future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Ikebukuro Incident and this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,public opinion is leaning in a harsher direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Protests Intensify After Introduction\N{\an8}of Red-Eye Protection Bill
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red-eye Protection Bill was submitted to the Diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4}Vampires Really Do Exist!! Segregate Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but all it will do is place more restrictions on devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Segregate Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In the current political climate, the police had\Nno choice but to deal with it the way they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if I had my way, I want you\Nand Anzai to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A human-devil couple like you two
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,would be a symbol of hope for\Nthose of us who want to coexist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So F Squad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked them to come up with a way\Nto lighten your punishment, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If something like this were to happen again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd kill Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils just don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,deserve to live with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I always knew... devils were just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to comment on\Nyour relationship with Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't have an answer to\Nwhether or not we can coexist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want us all to be able to live our lives together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It is what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to talk to Taira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:17:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you and Anzai will be banned from making\Nany contact with each other whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything you want to tell him,\Nyou have until then to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to her? What would I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai, have you had any more flashbacks\Nsince we last talked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I met Kikuhara at ONLO.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He took me to the basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and showed me my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was a devil and a mass-murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father, Tamaki Anzai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,had a human girlfriend before he met your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was killed by a bunch of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki took revenge on the men who killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But after he drank the blood of\Nhis victims, he lost control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed 10 more innocent people,\Npassersby and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd lost his love, murdered 15 people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time they brought him to ONLO,\Nhe was a living corpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,ruled by his addiction to blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother knew that's the kind of man he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what she ever saw in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me she can't explain it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But from the first time they met...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...he was always on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the time I saw him again, I had fallen in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be a devil, but that's not all you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fixate on just one part of yourself,\Nyour thoughts skew too far in one direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Be brave and face the woman you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear about my punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you called me out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I really had to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so close to finding the key to\Nconfronting the devil inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd had a little more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have... found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have found hope... found a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't given me your blood, I would have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have made it this far without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lost you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like everything I've gained\Nwill slip through my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I always hated the devil inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I always hated myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, when you said you liked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your smile was so blindingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't quite accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you let me hear it, just one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How you feel about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look me in the eye and say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If Anzai is moving forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll move forward, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:21:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sotto tokete yuku you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Motto ai shiaetara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nani o tsutaerareta no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai o tsumugenai meguriawase
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dare ka yurushite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kegareta sugata ga boku de aru koto o
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Aa doushite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fureru yubi ga furueteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's story of fight together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakishimetai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizu tsukezu ni mamoritai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Anata dake o
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.09,0:21:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's story of desire forever
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aragai tsuzukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakiagaru shoudou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aa, mata boku wa..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep red dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sotto futari tokete yuku you ni...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.63,0:22:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I like your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.09,0:22:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Very cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:22:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,more beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}The Potential for Human and Red-Eye Coexistence
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Tsukasa Taira